{"tid":2490871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連鎖店賣欠標籤貨 海關無執法","createTime":"2021-04-16T02:31:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T22:44:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8f7e6dbae740f65d70862ac4670188432d6452bd","tid":2490871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/M37D5M4Y6VDXVDRBNDFJA7ULQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FM37D5M4Y6VDXVDRBNDFJA7ULQA%2F&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwDQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=339fc4ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210416%2FM37D5M4Y6VDXVDRBNDFJA7ULQA%2F&h=93367051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210416/M37D5M4Y6VDXVDRBNDFJA7ULQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n連鎖店賣欠標籤貨 海關無執法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JPQuwHjpXeGc5e_KRNPZEo2SbTM=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ICTKBH6QN5DOVNAW65BWQZMN5Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJPQuwHjpXeGc5e_KRNPZEo2SbTM%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FICTKBH6QN5DOVNAW65BWQZMN5Q.jpg&h=e81367b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■記者昨到淘大商場的大生生活超市，發現貨架上有洗頭水未貼雙語標籤。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海關上周四高調搜查阿布泰國生活百貨，以未有按消費品安全條例貼上中英文警告標籤為由，撿取逾8,800件貨品並拘捕公司董事。事件引發不少大型連鎖雜貨店臨急抱佛腳，連日急急為貨品貼上中英文標籤，事發至昨日踏入第八日，市面仍有連鎖店被發現繼續售賣未貼中英文標籤的清潔護理用品，海關只稱收到舉報，卻未見有實際掃蕩行動。<br />\n<br />\n在海關大舉掃蕩阿布泰門市及倉庫，指其售賣的清潔用品未按消費品安全條例貼上中。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者昨到牛頭角淘大商場的大生生活超市巡視，發現至少三款洗頭水、兩款身體潤膚露、兩款。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿布泰感謝市民力撐<br />\n<br />\n阿布泰昨晚在fb指「一連7日阿布泰潑水節感謝禮今晚就告一段落」，感謝眾多商戶夥伴及市民支持，今日休息一天，「香港人！星期六再見」！海關指上周五至周三接獲290宗涉及產品安全標籤的舉報，涉及不同連鎖零售店集團和個別零售店舖，正跟進並安排巡查及試購，如發現違規會採取執法行動。"},{"pid":"19d81f4a435f9a326feef4a77616eb6198c910a3","tid":2490871,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:38:50.000Z","msg":"班公墓員而家面皮同777一樣厚，任你點屌佢都面不改容，成個款就係到講：我擺撚明係選擇執法你吹撚脹"},{"pid":"e65a675b518e1e795d9aebeaa826438b202f2aff","tid":2490871,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T02:59:22.000Z","msg":"黑關"},{"pid":"1fcf133cdb00b3b971e31ad52888ee4bfc09b81d","tid":2490871,"uid":27432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T03:01:26.000Z","msg":"海關好黃?"},{"pid":"757e51d63dff581357506979a9d20c56f34caf1e","tid":2490871,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"130dea9306e723b7e5a8a6f50dfce2bf87a7123e","tid":2490871,"uid":257533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:34:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb45e6e80b21f88ddc2e7dc3fd44a2e93afc2bb7","tid":2490871,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35cfa33d7df4c65fae67915c470df0b5e65840ce","tid":2490871,"uid":275384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}